      "item": "emit_untracked_requirements",
      "reviewed": false,
      "intent": "Emit Untracked diagnostics for requirements found in source but absent from any sidecar. When --fix is active and not dry-run, create or update the co-located .liyi.jsonc sidecar for each source file with missing RequirementSpec entries, using the full requirement span from marker pairing and populating source_anchor from the source text.",
