      "item": "check_trivial_ignore",
      "reviewed": true,
      "intent": "Emit Trivial or Ignored info diagnostics for @liyi:trivial and @liyi:ignore markers within the item's span. For the sidecar =trivial sentinel, emit Trivial info unless @liyi:nontrivial is present in the span, in which case emit ConflictingTriviality error.",
